original_title: Sesame Street - I'm Glad I'm Me
overview: I'm Glad I'm Me is a 1986 Sesame Street video compilation in the "My Sesame Street Home Video" series. Maria reads a story called I'm Glad I'm Me, which Big Bird and Grundgetta act out, playing the roles of Prince Charmingbird and Princess Grouchy, respectively. In this story, they learn about self-esteem and parts of the body.
title: Sesame Street - I'm Glad I'm Me
